<p>Hello <%= @freelancer.name %>,</p>

<p>You have submitted changes for the task "<strong><%= @task.title %></strong>".</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Task ID:</strong> <%= @task.id %></li>
  <li><strong>Title:</strong> <%= @task.title %></li>
  <li><strong>Deadline:</strong> <%= @task.deadline ? @task.deadline.strftime("%B %d, %Y") : "Not set" %></li>
  <li><strong>Status:</strong> <%= @task.status.capitalize %></li>
</ul>

<p>The client (<%= @task.client.name %>) has been notified of your submitted changes. Feel free to communicate with them directly in case further revisions are required.</p>

<p>Thank you for your professionalism!</p>